OL,3,CEden Project cuts 80 jobs to 'ensure
OL,4,Clong-term economic stability'
OL,6,FOne of Cornwall's most iconic tourist
OL,7,Fattractions has announced plans to cut
OL,8,Fdozens of jobs amid financial
OL,9,Fpressures.
OL,11,FThe Eden Project at Bodelva, near St
OL,12,FAustell, has confirmed it will cut
OL,13,Fapproximately 20 per cent of its
OL,14,Fworkforce - which equates to up to 80
OL,15,Froles.
OL,17,FIt is the second wave of job losses at
OL,18,Fthe venue in less than two years, and
OL,19,Fcomes amid a drop in tourism numbers
OL,20,Fto the region.
