OL,3,CEden Project cuts 80 jobs to 'ensure
OL,4,Clong-term economic stability'
OL,6,FAn Eden Project spokesperson said the
OL,7,F"proactive measures" will ensure the
OL,8,F"long-term economic stability" of the
OL,9,Fbusiness.
OL,11,F'Considerable economic challenges' -
OL,12,FEden Project
OL,14,F"We have explored every option and
OL,15,Fwill create a new structure as a
OL,16,Fresult of considerable economic
OL,17,Fchallenges," the spokesperson said.
