OL,3,CEden Project cuts 80 jobs to 'ensure
OL,4,Clong-term economic stability'
OL,6,F"This will involve reducing our
OL,7,Fpayroll by an estimated 20 per cent,
OL,8,Fequivalent to around 80 redundancies,
OL,9,Fincluding 19 who have elected to leave
OL,10,Fvoluntarily (through voluntary
OL,11,Fredundancy or retirement).
OL,13,F"A number of factors including the
OL,14,Fcontraction of the visitor economy
OL,15,Facross the south west as well as
OL,16,Fsignificantly increased costs to
OL,17,Fbusinesses have made this process
OL,18,Fnecessary.
